<p>Meglev is the most modern land transportation on the planet, the top speed is around 433 KM/H, so it only takes 7 minutes from Shanghai Metro Line 2 to <a href="http://io.v2ex.com/shanghai/shanghai-airports.html" target="_blank">Pudong International Airport</a>. The ticket price of Meglev is 50 RMB for single trip, 100 RMB for round trip. If you have a air ticket then the ticket price is 20% off.</p>